span.p:
Security Policy
|
VLAN 1011 (Public LAN): Tunnel Server - most restricted, only outbound initiated
|
VLAN 1010 (App LAN): Web-facing services - allow inbound from Public, outbound to Data on specific ports
|
VLAN 1012 (Data LAN): Backend services - no direct inbound from Public, only from App on specific ports
|
Management: SSH from Admin Desktop across all VLANs
